.TH "TODOPRO ENCRYPTION SETUP" "1" "2026-02-27" "1.0.0" "todopro encryption setup Manual"
.SH NAME
todopro\-encryption\-setup \- Set up end-to-end encryption for the first...
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B todopro encryption setup
[OPTIONS]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Set up end-to-end encryption for the first time.
.PP
This will:
1. Generate a new master encryption key
2. Display your 24-word recovery phrase (SAVE THIS!)
3. Verify you saved the recovery phrase
4. Store the key locally and backup to server
